{
  "video_id": "Nmg0_nBdBRg",
  "title": "When is \"eavesdropping\" a crime? (Penal Code 632)",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6210.0,
      "end_time": 9930.0,
      "text": "As a former prosecutor and now criminal defense lawyer, people"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9930.0,
      "end_time": 12790.0,
      "text": "ask me all the time, what is eavesdropping?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12790.0,
      "end_time": 15649.0,
      "text": "Or when is eavesdropping illegal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 15650.0,
      "end_time": 17450.0,
      "text": "And the legal definition of eavesdropping"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 17450.0,
      "end_time": 19860.0,
      "text": "here in California is when you listen"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19860.0,
      "end_time": 23680.0,
      "text": "in on a private conversation without the knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 23680.0,
      "end_time": 27550.0,
      "text": "or consent of the parties and you use either a recording"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27550.0,
      "end_time": 32250.0,
      "text": "device to record the conversation or an amplifying"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32250.0,
      "end_time": 34940.0,
      "text": "device to help you hear the conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34940.0,
      "end_time": 36190.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;ll give you an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36190.0,
      "end_time": 38379.0,
      "text": "Suppose you&#39;re in the bathroom stall at work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38380.0,
      "end_time": 41530.0,
      "text": "and two co-workers come in and they start talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41530.0,
      "end_time": 43530.0,
      "text": "about some confidential matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43530.0,
      "end_time": 46490.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t realize you&#39;re in the bathroom stall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46490.0,
      "end_time": 49890.0,
      "text": "and you just quietly overhear their conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49890.0,
      "end_time": 51870.0,
      "text": "That is not eavesdropping."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51870.0,
      "end_time": 54640.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s at least not illegal eavesdropping"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54640.0,
      "end_time": 56900.0,
      "text": "as the law defines it because you&#39;re not"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56900.0,
      "end_time": 59519.0,
      "text": "using any sort of device to amplify or record"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59520.0,
      "end_time": 61600.0,
      "text": "the conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61600.0,
      "end_time": 63370.0,
      "text": "But suppose you take out your iPhone and you decide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63370.0,
      "end_time": 64890.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to take advantage of this opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64890.0,
      "end_time": 66556.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to record what they&#39;re saying."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66556.0,
      "end_time": 68130.0,
      "text": "And you record their conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68130.0,
      "end_time": 72130.0,
      "text": "Then it becomes eavesdropping, and that would be illegal."
    }
  ]
}